      "copy": "You arrive at the Bruised Banana. A quiet house in Portland where something unusual is underway. Laptops open on tables. Whiteboards filled with fragments of strategy. Someone left a mug of tea beside a stack of notes. You've stepped into the early days of a three-month build experiment.",
