      "type": "prompt",
      "copy": "The work happening here began as a book called ''Mastering the Game of Allyship''. Over time the idea outgrew the page. The framework started behaving like a game — something people could step into together. Conversations became quests. Emotional shifts turned into visible moves. Coordination bec...",
