    },
    {
      "id": "The Turning Point",
      "type": "prompt",
      "copy": "Over the past year small groups have tested this system. The largest run happened on February 21 during a birthday gathering. Dozens of players entered the story at once. The system held. Two weeks later the circumstances of my life shifted in a way that created space to focus on building this wo...",
