    },
    {
      "id": "The Invitation",
      "type": "prompt",
      "copy": "You've arrived while this next chapter is beginning. Some people will help build the system. Some will test it by playing. Some will support the residency so the work can continue. Before you step further into the campaign, there's a simple question. How does this land for you?",
